What you need to know:

Eager to get the ticket for the world junior competition due August 17 to 22 next year at Kasarani, Kibet took the Nyayo National Stadium’s red tartan track by storm, to win in eight minutes and 43.7 secondsKorir said they plan to have a specialised training for sprints and field events in December and April next year where the athletes will train a bubble with some of the country's best coachesFederation’s youth committee chairman Korir plans specialised training for sprints, field events